## Quality Standards

Generated UI code must:
- ✅ Follow `coding-standards.md` conventions
- ✅ Respect `tech-stack.md` approved technologies
- ✅ Place files according to `source-tree.md` structure
- ✅ Use dependencies from `dependencies.md` only
- ✅ Avoid patterns listed in `anti-patterns.md`
- ✅ Include accessibility attributes (ARIA, alt text)
- ✅ Follow best practices from references/
- ✅ Be properly commented and documented
- ✅ Match story acceptance criteria (if story provided)

